name: Super Baby Prototype
description:
This is a Game I am reworking on going to remake the game again and make it better then this prototype made last year, its pretty much your basic mario game.

Buttons are
left arrow - Move Left
right arrow - Move Right
Up Arrow - Jump & doublejump

FYI The game still has a bunch of game breaking bugs in it at the moment
In case you in counter one please press the R button to restart the the level your on

if you wish to stay updated on this project please checkout the youtube link below:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLia9SaEmP2XIQzXWc2UmI2Q_JOLMz0p9q
